@startuml sequence-tc2-visitor-between-pois
title TC2 — Visitor giữa 2 POI: Admin xem + Xung đột ưu tiên
skinparam defaultFontSize 11

== Phần A: Admin xem vị trí du khách tương đối với POI ==

actor       "Du khách"   as U
participant "DeviceHub"  as Hub
database    "DB"         as DB
participant "GET /nearby-pois" as API
actor       "Admin Web"  as Admin

U    -> Hub : SendLocation(DEV-001, lat, lng)
Hub  -> DB  : UPDATE GuestDevices SET LastLatitude, LastLongitude

Admin -> API : GET /api/v1/admin/devices/DEV-001/nearby-pois
API  -> DB   : SELECT GuestDevice + SELECT Pois WHERE IsActive
API  -> API  : HaversineDistance(device, poi)\nfilter dist ≤ 500m
API --> Admin : [{ name:"POI-A", dist:95m, withinRadius:true },\n { name:"POI-B", dist:80m, withinRadius:true }]
Admin -> Admin : Hiện popup "POI gần" ● POI-A ● POI-B

== Phần B: Xung đột khi đứng giữa 2 POI — Winner-Only ==

actor "Du khách" as DU
participant "NarrationMgr" as Nar
participant "Audio/TTS"    as Audio

DU -> Nar : HandleAsync(POI-A, level=2)
note right of Nar : Queue rỗng → POI-A thắng
Nar -> Audio : Play POI-A 🔊

DU -> Nar : HandleAsync(POI-B, level=1)
note right of Nar : POI-A (level=2) > POI-B (level=1)\n→ Loại bỏ POI-B ✗
Nar --> DU : discarded

Audio --> DU : 🔊 Chỉ nghe POI-A
@enduml
